Show HN: ChatGPT in Your Menubar
text:
I have been enjoying using ChatGPT as my AI assistant and improving my workflow. So I thought it would be nice to have it readily available without having to switch to my browser.

This is just attempt one. Will be adding more functionality such as keyboard shortcuts and voice input in the future.

Would a transparent pile of compost the size of the Sun have the same effect?
text:
I followed a thread here that included the surprising fact that Hydrogen fusion is so unlikely the power output per volume of the core of the sun is only about the same as a compost heap.

The reason the sun is so bright and hot is its size.
